s/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:3187:\"<p>In tutta Italia ci sono meetup WordPress!</p><p>I meetup sono <strong>incontri gratuiti e aperti a tutti,</strong> in cui le community locali si incontrano per condividere conoscenze, conoscersi e fare rete.</p><p>Se non sai cos’è un meetup <a href=\"https://it.wordpress.org/meetup/guida-ai-meetup-di-wordpress/\">leggi qui.</a></p><p>Tutti i meetup WordPress italiani attivi sono <a href=\"https://it.wordpress.org/meetup/\">elencati qui.</a></p><p><strong>Nei prossimi giorni, <em>in ordine cronologico</em>, si incontrano le community di:</strong></p><h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Milano</h2><p>mer 11 dic, ore 19:00, &#8220;Sessione aperta domande e risposte&#8221; &#8211; <a href=\"https://www.meetup.com/wordpress-meetup-milano/events/304709729\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">iscriviti qui per partecipare</a></p><h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Reggio Emilia</h2><p>gio 12 dic, ore 18:30, &#8220;Reggio Emilia WP MeetUp La cassetta degli attrezzi del marketer&#8221; &#8211; <a href=\"https://www.meetup.com/reggio-emilia-wordpress-meetup/events/304914111\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">iscriviti qui per partecipare</a></p><h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Treviso</h2><p>gio 12 dic, ore 19:30, &#8220;Pizza di fine anno Treviso WordPress Meetup&#8221; &#8211; <a href=\"https://www.meetup.com/treviso-wordpress-meetup/events/304999905\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">iscriviti qui per partecipare</a></p><h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Roma</h2><p>ven 13 dic, ore 18:30, &#8220;Ask me anything about WordPress + cena di Natale&#8221; &#8211; <a href=\"https://www.meetup.com/romawordpress/events/304882472\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">iscriviti qui per partecipare</a></p><h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Genova</h2><p>lun 16 dic, ore 20:00, &#8220;Cena di fine anno in pizzeria!&#8221; &#8211; <a href=\"https://www.meetup.com/wordpress-meetup-genova/events/304894658\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">iscriviti qui per partecipare</a></p><h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Verona</h2><p>mar 17 dic, ore 19:00, &#8220;WordPress Meetup Verona #70 Strumentie risorse che facilitano il lavoro&#8221; &#8211; <a href=\"https://www.meetup.com/verona-wordpress-meetup/events/305005294\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">iscriviti qui per partecipare</a></p><h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Pisa</h2><p>mer 18 dic, ore 18:00, &#8220;WordPress go live: Il Tuo Sito Ovunque in Pochi Minuti&#8221; &#8211; <a href=\"https://www.meetup.com/pisa-wordpress-meetup/events/305012538\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">iscriviti qui per partecipare</a></p><h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Catania</h2><p>gio 19 dic, ore 19:00, &#8220;WordPress Meetup Catania Dicembre 2024: Performance&#8221; &#8211; <a href=\"https://www.meetup.com/meetup-wordpress-catania/events/304842161\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">iscriviti qui per partecipare</a></p><div style=\"height:var(--wp--preset--spacing--50)\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div><p class=\"has-text-align-center has-dark-blueberry-color has-blueberry-3-background-color has-text-color has-background has-link-color has-extra-large-font-size\">… articolo in aggiornamento…</p>\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:75:\"https://it.wordpress.org/news/2024/12/tutti-i-meetup-di-dicembre-2024/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:30:\"com-wordpress:feed-additions:1\";a:1:{s:7:\"post-i